---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import avatar from "../assets/avatar.jpg";

const url = new URL(Astro.url);
const avatarParameter = url.searchParams.get("avatar");
---

<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto my-10 bg-white p-8 rounded-lg">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-8 gap-4">
    <div class="col-span-6">
      <section>
        <div class="text-2xl font-semibold">Stas Strugovshchikov</div>
        <div>Frontend Developer</div>
        <div class="text-sm">Orlando, FL, 🇺🇸 United States</div>
      </section>

      <section class="mt-3">
        <p class="text-sm mt-1">📞 +1 (786) 325 4891</p>
        <p class="text-sm mt-1">✉️ stanislav.stru@gmail.com</p>
        <div class="flex gap-3 divide-x divide-gray-500 mt-1 text-sm">
          <span class="pr-3">
            🔗 <a
              href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/strugovshchikov"
              target="_blank"
              class="text-blue-600">LinkedIn</a
            >
          </span>
          <span>
            🔗 <a
              href="https://github.com/stanislavstru"
              target="_blank"
              class="text-blue-600">GitHub</a
            >
          </span>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
    {
      avatarParameter && (
        <div class="col-span-2">
          <Image
            src={avatar}
            alt="Stanislav Strugovshchikov"
            class="rounded-lg"
          />
        </div>
      )
    }
  </div>

  <section class="mt-5">
    <p class="text-sm">
      Highly skilled and driven Front-end developer with 10+ years of experience
      in managing web application development with server logic, utilizing
      creating responsive & user-friendly designs. Proven expertise in building
      AI-powered applications in collaborating with cross-functional teams,
      integrating LLM-based solutions, and developing intelligent automation
      tools.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-4">
    <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl">Experience</h2>

    <div class="ml-3 mt-1 text-sm">
      <div class="mt-2">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Frontend Developer</h3>
        <a class="inline-block" href="https://www.criya.co/" target="_blank"
          ><h3 class="text-md font-bold">Criya</h3></a
        >
        <p class="text-gray-600">June 2022 to February 2025 (2 yrs 9 mos)</p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
          <li>
            The project was migrated from Ruby to Next.js, resulting in a 100%
            increase in performance and improved search engine rankings.
          </li>
          <li>
            Integrated LLM mechanisms and AI Agent workflows to enable
            end-to-end personalized AI-driven marketing campaigns in under 60
            seconds
          </li>
          <li>
            Implemented 15 different third-party payment, analytics, auth
            integrations
          </li>
          <li>
            Designed a monorepo-based architecture with modular application
            separation. Established a reusable codebase, significantly improving
            project performance.
          </li>
          <li>
            Developed a style library that was later used for all new project
            integrations.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-4">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Frontend Developer</h3>
        <a class="inline-block" href="https://dzsystems.ru/en/" target="_blank"
          ><h3 class="text-md font-bold">DZ Systems</h3></a
        >
        <p class="text-gray-600">February 2021 - June 2022 (1 year 5 months)</p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
          <li>
            Developed a social network for business professionals and
            implemented a WebSockets-based chat system for negotiation
            coordination, reducing the process to just 3 steps globally
          </li>
          <li>Built microservices architecture for high scalability.</li>
          <li>Localized the project into 5 languages.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-4">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Software Engineer</h3>
        <a
          class="inline-block"
          href="https://pro.myseldon.com/en/promo"
          target="_blank"><h3 class="text-md font-bold">Seldon Pro</h3></a
        >
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          January 2020 - February 2021 (1 year 2 months)
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
          <li>
            Migrated legacy projects from jQuery to Next.js, increasing
            efficiency by 200%.
          </li>
          <li>
            Established a configuration rule for collaboration between designers
            and front-end developers, tripling development speed.
          </li>
          <li>
            Introduced modern CSS frameworks to enhance styling and
            maintainability.
          </li>
          <li>
            Established seamless collaboration between C# developers and the
            Front-end team.
          </li>
          <li>
            Optimized PostgreSQL database performance by 37% without changing
            the number of queried parameters
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-4">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Full-Stack Developer</h3>
        <a class="inline-block" href="https://mebelidomanet.ru/" target="_blank"
          ><h3 class="text-md font-bold">Mebelidomanet</h3></a
        >

        <p class="text-gray-600">April 2017 - May 2020 (3 years 2 months)</p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
          <li>
            I have successfully developed several big marketplaces, including a
            market place in Russia, namely a core platform on which 147 online
            shops were built. Used Yii2.
          </li>
          <li>
            Collaborated on designing a structure for fast database queries.
          </li>
          <li>
            Our team worked on SEO optimization, resulting in over 43% of our
            websites ranking in the top 1-3 positions.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-4">
    <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl">Skills</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-1 text-sm">
      <li>
        <strong>Frontend:</strong> TypeScript, React, Next.js, Astro.js, Redux, TailwindCSS,
        Microservices, NX, WebSockets, REST API, Responsive Layout (CSS Grid, Flexbox)
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Mobile:</strong> Ionic, React Native, Capacitor
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>DevOps & Tools:</strong> Nginx, Unix, Docker, AWS, Firebase, Vercel,
        Jenkins
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>AI & Integrations:</strong> OpenAI API, ChatGPT, Stripe API, Google
        API and etc.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Other:</strong> Node.js, Express, NestJS, PHP (Yii2, Symfony), PostgreSQL,
        MongoDB, MySQL, GraphQL, Wordpress
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-4">
    <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl">Education</h2>
    <p class="ml-3 mt-1 text-sm">
      <strong>Russia, Nizhniy Novgorod, State Technical University</strong> (2007
      - 2012)
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-6 text-center text-sm">
    <p>🚀 Open to new opportunities and collaborations!</p>
  </section>
</div>
